      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;ancestral-unique-gloves-gloves-of-the-illuminator&#34;&gt;[Ancestral Unique Gloves] Gloves of The Illuminator &lt;a href=&#34;#ancestral-unique-gloves-gloves-of-the-illuminator&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;material-icons align-middle&#34;&gt;link&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;925 Item Power&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;462 Armor&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;+[9.0 - 11.0]% Critical Strike Chance&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;+[10.5 - 15.0]% Fireball Attack Speed (Sorcerer Only)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;+[1 - 2] Mana when a Fireball Explodes&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;+[2 - 3]% to Fireball (Sorcerer Only)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Requires Level: 80&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;div markdown=&#34;span&#34; class=&#34;bs-callout-v2 bs-callout-v2-warning bs-callout-v2-level-1&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    Fireball now bounces as it travels, exploding each time it hits the ground, but its explosion deals [30 - 0]% less damage. (Sorcerer Only)&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;  &#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;div markdown=&#34;span&#34; class=&#34;bs-callout-v2 bs-callout-v2-secdondary bs-callout-v2-level-1&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    After Inarius returned to Sanctuary, he sought a way back to the High Heavens. His first step was to reignite the religion he had abandoned millennia before: the Cathedral of Light.&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;  &#xA;&lt;figure&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;https://cloudlog.kr/images/game/diablo/db/item/gloves/diablo4-item-ancestral-unique-gloves-gloves-of-the-illuminator-01-en.jpg&#34; width=&#34;372&#34; alt=&#34;[Diablo 4] Ancestral Unique Gloves [Gloves of The Illuminator] Info&#34; class=&#39;docimage&#39;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;document-update-history&#34;&gt;Document Update History &lt;a href=&#34;#document-update-history&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34; aria-hidden=&